            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] mb-1">SEN Support (Special Educational Needs)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">We enrol children with additional needs on a case-by-case basis and offer specialised support as needed, with additional charges. Please request the "SEN Support Fees" document for details.</p>
